SELECT 
    asp.*, 
    ani.ani001_animal 
FROM "{{JSutils.currentSchema()}}".hotaspecto001 AS asp
INNER JOIN "{{JSutils.currentSchema()}}".hotani001 AS ani 
    ON asp.aspecto001_tipoanimal = ani.ani001_id 
WHERE asp.aspecto001_deleted <> true 
    AND asp.aspecto001_descricao ILIKE '%{{TableAspectos.searchText}}%'
ORDER BY
{{
  ({
    aspecto001_descricao: 'asp.aspecto001_descricao',
    aspecto001_id: 'asp.aspecto001_id',
    aspecto001_tipoanimal: 'asp.aspecto001_tipoanimal'
  }[TableAspectos.sortOrder.column]) || 'asp.aspecto001_descricao'
}}
{{ TableAspectos.sortOrder.order === 'DESC' ? 'DESC' : 'ASC' }}
LIMIT {{TableAspectos.pageSize}}
OFFSET {{(TableAspectos.pageNo - 1) * TableAspectos.pageSize}};
